## 🌍 Server & Utility Commands

### `/reloadcfg`
**Description:** Reloads PalDefender configuration (`Config.json`, `whitelist.json`) and refreshes the Palworld banlist (`banlist.txt`).
**Arguments:** None
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/pgbroadcast`
**Description:** Sends a message to all players on the server. Unlike the vanilla broadcast, this supports spaces.
**Syntax:** `/pgbroadcast <message>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`
**Example:** `/pgbroadcast Server will restart soon.`

### `/alert`
**Description:** Shows big, red, important text on everyone's screen (similar to meteor text). Use `\n` for multi-lines.
**Syntax:** `/alert <message>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/send`
**Description:** Sends a specific type of message to a specific player.
**Syntax:** `/send <type> <UserId> <Message>`
**Arguments:**
* `<type>`: `msg` (chat), `log` (white, quick), `ilog` (blue, longer), `vilog` (blue, extremely long).
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/settime`
**Description:** Sets the time of day.
**Syntax:** `/settime <hour>`
**Arguments:** `0-23`, `day`, or `night`.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/adminlogin` & `/adminlogout`
**Description:** Logs you into or out of admin mode. `/adminlogin` is an alias for `/adminpassword`.
**Syntax:** `/adminlogin <password>` | `/adminlogout`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `Admin`

### `/addadminip`
**Description:** Adds an IP address to the admin whitelist.
**Syntax:** `/addadminip <IP>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/iwantplayerlist`
**Description:** Enables the in-game player list overlay (press ESC to view Player UIDs and UserIds).
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/getrconcmds`
**Description:** Returns a list of all available RCON commands and their argument counts.
**Permissions:** `RCON`

### `/getskinids` (formerly `/skins`)
**Description:** Returns a list of all available Pal Skin IDs. RCON receives JSON output.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/gettechids`
**Description:** Returns a list of all available technology IDs. RCON receives JSON output.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

