## 📍 Teleportation & Movement

### `/tp`
**Description:** Highly versatile teleport command for moving players, self, or reaching POIs.
**Syntax Variations:**
* `/tp <X> <Y> [Z]` - Teleport yourself to map coordinates.
* `/tp <UserId>` - Teleport yourself to a player.
* `/tp home` - Teleport to your nearest BaseCamp.
* `/tp oilrig` - Teleport to the nearest OilRig.
* `/tp oilrig:Lv30` - Teleport to a specific OilRig (`Lv30`, `Lv55`, `Lv60`).
* `/tp <UserID1> <UserID2>` - Teleport User 1 to User 2 (RCON supported).
* `/tp <UserID> <X> <Y> <Z>` - Teleport a player to coordinates.
* `/tp <UserID> home` - Teleport a player to their closest base.
* `/tp <UserID> oilrig` - Teleport a player to closest OilRig.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/getpos`
**Description:** Gets current world position. Useful for teleporting/summoning.
**Syntax:** `/getpos [UserId]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

