## 🏰 Base, Guild & OilRig Operations

### `/getnearestbase`
**Description:** Shows the guild name and UID of the nearest base using map coordinates. RCON requires X, Y, Z.
**Syntax:** `/getnearestbase [X] [Y] [Z]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/gotonearestbase`
**Description:** Teleports you to the nearest base.
**Syntax:** `/gotonearestbase [X] [Y] [Z]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `Admin`

### `/killnearestbase`
**Description:** Destroys the nearest base. **Use with caution!**
**Syntax:** `/killnearestbase [X] [Y] [Z]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/setguildleader`
**Description:** Sets the target player as the leader of their current guild.
**Syntax:** `/setguildleader <UserId>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/exportguilds`
**Description:** Exports guild data (Map/World positions, GuildChest, Expeditions, etc.) to `guildexport.json`.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/resetoilrig`
**Description:** Resets OilRig boxes and enemies.
**Syntax:** `/resetoilrig <oilrig>`
**Arguments:** `lv30`, `lv55`, `lv60`, or `all`.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

