## 🎒 Items & Inventory

### `/give` & `/giveme`
**Description:** Gives items to a player or yourself.
**Syntax:** `/give <UserId> <ItemID> [Amount=1]` | `/giveme <ItemID> [Amount=1]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin` (give) | `Chat`, `Admin` (giveme)

### `/giveitems`
**Description:** Gives multiple items in one command separated by spaces, with amounts separated by colons.
**Syntax:** `/giveitems <UserId> <ItemId>[:<Amount>] ...`
**Example:** `/giveitems steam_123 Sword:2 Shield:1`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/delitem` & `/delitems`
**Description:** Removes items from a player's inventory. Setting amount to `0` shows the count without deleting. Use `all` to delete all occurrences.
**Syntax:** `/delitem <UserId> <ItemID> <Amount>` | `/delitems <UserId> <ItemId>[:<Amount>] ...`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/give_relic` & `/giveme_relic`
**Description:** Gives Lifmunk Effigies (use a negative number to subtract).
**Syntax:** `/give_relic <UserId> <Amount>` | `/giveme_relic [Amount]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/clearinv`
**Description:** Clears specific containers from a player's inventory.
**Syntax:** `/clearinv <UserID> [Container:Array]`
**Arguments:** `items`, `keyitems`, `armor`, `weapons`, `food`, `dropslot`, or `all`.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

