## 🐾 Pals & Eggs

### `/givepal` & `/givemepal`
**Description:** Gives a Pal with random stats/passives at the specified level. Use the Pal's developer name (e.g., `WeaselDragon`).
**Syntax:** `/givepal <UserId> <PalID> [Level=1]` | `/givemepal <PalID> [Level=1]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/givepal_j` & `/givemepal_j`
**Description:** Gives a Pal defined by a PalTemplate JSON file (supports SkinId). Embedded JSON is no longer supported; use the filename.
**Syntax:** `/givepal_j <UserId> <PalTemplate>` | `/givemepal_j <PalTemplate>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/spawnpal` & `/spawnpal_j`
**Description:** Spawns a wild Pal. RCON requires X, Y, Z coordinates.
**Syntax:** `/spawnpal <PalID> [X] [Y] [Z] [Level=1]` | `/spawnpal_j <PalTemplate> [X] [Y] [Z]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/deletepals`
**Description:** Deletes Pals from a user utilizing advanced string filters.
**Syntax:** `/deletepals <UserId> <PalFilter>`
**Filters:** Combine keywords like `ID`, `Nick`, `Gender`, `Level`, `Rank`, `Lucky`, `Passives`, and `Limit`.
**Example:** `/deletepals steam_123 ID Anubis Rank>=3`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/exportpals`
**Description:** Exports equipped Pals to a template file.
**Syntax:** `/exportpals [UserId]`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/removedroppedpals`
**Description:** Removes all Pals currently dropped in the world.
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### Special Admin Pals
* `/jetragon`: Gives you an Admin Jetragon (Max level, extremely fast).
* `/catwaifu`: Gives you an Admin Cat Waifu (Buffs character stats, max level).

### Egg Commands
**Description:** Gives an egg with a specific Pal inside. Size ranges from `01` to `05` (e.g., `PalEgg_Fire_01`).
* `/giveegg <UserID> <EggID> <PalID> [Level=1]`
* `/givemeegg <EggID> <PalID> [Level=1]`
* `/giveegg_j <UserID> <EggID> <PalTemplate> [Level=1]`
* `/givemeegg_j <EggID> <PalTemplate> [Level=1]`

