## 📈 Experience, Stats & Technology

### `/give_exp` & `/giveme_exp`
**Description:** Gives experience points. (Note: Gives in a small radius around the target player).
**Syntax:** `/give_exp <UserId> <Amount>` | `/giveme_exp <Amount>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### `/givestats` & `/givemestats`
**Description:** Gives unused stat points. Negative subtracts. Default `0` displays unused points.
**Syntax:** `/givestats <UserId> <numStats>` | `/givemestats <numStats>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`

### Technology & Ancient Tech
**Description:** Grant technology points (negative subtracts).
* `/givetech <UserId> [Count]` / `/givemetech [Count]`
* `/givebosstech <UserId> [Count]` / `/givemebosstech [Count]`

### `/learntech` & `/unlearntech`
**Description:** Lets a player learn or forget a specific technology. TechID can be `all`.
**Syntax:** `/learntech <UserID> <TechID>` | `/unlearntech <UserID> <TechID>`
**Permissions:** `Chat`, `RCON`, `Admin`
